verses.text:
For her wound \add is\add* incurable; for it is come unto Judah;
he is come unto the gate of my people, \add even\add* to Jerusalem.\f + \fr 1.9 
\ft her…: or, she is grievously sick of her wounds\f*

Therefore thus saith the \nd LORD\nd*; Behold, against this
family do I devise an evil, from which ye shall not remove your necks;
neither shall ye go haughtily: for this time \add is\add* evil.

In that day, saith the \nd LORD\nd*, will I assemble her that
halteth, and I will gather her that is driven out, and her that I have
afflicted;

O my people, remember now what Balak king of Moab consulted,
and what Balaam the son of Beor answered him from Shittim unto Gilgal;
that ye may know the righteousness of the \nd LORD\nd*.

For the son dishonoureth the father, the daughter riseth up
against her mother, the daughter in law against her mother in law;
a man’s enemies \add are\add* the men of his own house.
